{"tid":1295370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix 為香港人打氣 上架Braveheart 對抗暴政","createTime":"2019-07-08T04:02:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T04:14:29.000Z","uid":174752,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"ce92451c02949beb4d05a99545aedc7258720bf7","tid":1295370,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:02:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lEOOZDbMrgE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlEOOZDbMrgE&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=bf45796a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lEOOZDbMrgE</a><br />\n<br />\n「我看到一整支由我同胞組成的軍隊<br />\n在此抵抗暴政<br />\n你們身為自由人來此戰鬥<br />\n而此時此刻你們是自由的<br />\n你們要用那自由去做甚麼<br />\n你們會戰鬥嗎？」<br />\n<br />\n「不會  不會  不會<br />\n戰鬥 和那種軍隊戰鬥  絕不<br />\n我們會逃跑  會活下去」<br />\n<br />\n「沒錯，<br />\n戰鬥  你也許會死<br />\n逃跑  你會活下去<br />\n至少能活一陣<br />\n然後許多年後躺在床上奄奄一息<br />\n那時你會不會想用你茍且偷生來的歲月去換取<br />\n一個機會  就這麼一個機會<br />\n回到這里裏 告訴我們的敵人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">他們或許可以奪走我們的生命<br />\n但他們永遠無法奪走我們的自由</span></span>」"},{"pid":"da1d220677318dc313aed273e13b072d981ca9e8","tid":1295370,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:09:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0a7852c7e169251450e8d68399d9f1a21237cbd","tid":1295370,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:11:41.000Z","msg":"香港人加油"},{"pid":"7365ba0e653583867e6514c24d543dcc2a65bf30","tid":1295370,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce92451c02949beb4d05a99545aedc7258720bf7","tid":1295370,"uid":174752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T04:02:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/lEOOZDbMrgE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FlEOOZDbMrgE&d=JetPiwFZRsNB2TajAgP4V4PST22DtV%2BdF%2FIIxhOvvTQ%3D&h=bf45796a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/lEOOZDbMrgE</a><br />\n<br />\